{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-single-blog-js","path":"/blogs/isku-xirka-aaladaha-horumarka-iot-iyo-saameyntiisa-ku-leedahay-nolosha-casriga-ah","result":{"data":{"sanityBlog":{"slug":{"current":"isku-xirka-aaladaha-horumarka-iot-iyo-saameyntiisa-ku-leedahay-nolosha-casriga-ah"},"title":" Isku xirka Aaladaha – Horumarka IoT iyo Saameyntiisa Ku Leedahay Nolosha Casriga ah","publishedAt":"2026-04-11T11:45:00.000Z","_rawBody":[{"_key":"8c1dde14184d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"31b71d0bd9040","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Internet of Things (IoT), ama isku xirka aaladaha, ayaa sii xoogeysanaya sanad kasta iyadoo si degdeg ah u beddelaysa sida aan u noolnahay, u shaqeyno, iyo u isticmaalno teknoolojiyada. Sanadka 2024, teknoolojiyada IoT waxay leedahay saameyn cusub oo aad u weyn, iyadoo ay soo ifbaxayaan horumarro waaweyn sida AI ku xiran aaladaha geeska, isku xirka 5G, iyo aaladaha dijitaalka ah ee casriga ah."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"3f4d6def5b41","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e060077b068c0","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Edge Computing iyo AI"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"43acf5c1c60d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"fcf1ffa0b27b0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Edge computing waxay u dhaqaaqday dhanka adeegsiga ku xiran aaladaha IoT iyada oo ay taageerayaan AI (Artificial Intelligence). Aaladaha geeska (edge devices) waxay awood u leeyihiin inay xogta ku falanqeeyaan goobta, taas oo yaraysa waqtiga daahitaanka waxayna kordhisaa xawaaraha iyo waxtarka ("},{"_key":"fcf1ffa0b27b1","_type":"span","marks":["154f0b46e494"],"text":"IoT Analytics"},{"_key":"fcf1ffa0b27b2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", "},{"_key":"fcf1ffa0b27b3","_type":"span","marks":["dd4841b6345b"],"text":"Monnit"},{"_key":"fcf1ffa0b27b4","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":")."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"154f0b46e494","_type":"link","href":"https://iot-analytics.com/"},{"_key":"dd4841b6345b","_type":"link","href":"https://www.monnit.com/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"de488b02294b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"1e172da20c0e0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Horumarka AI iyo ML (Machine Learning) ayaa sidoo kale si weyn looga faa’iidaysan doonaa, iyadoo aaladaha IoT ee adeegsanaya barnaamijyada caqliga leh ay awood u leeyihiin inay si caqli leh ula falgalaan xogta ay helaan, taas oo sahlaysa maamulidda caqliga leh ee xogta waxaana ay kordhisaa waxtarka."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"dbeede2dfea0","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f06684d730570","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Isku Xirka 5G iyo Codsiyada IoT"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"9bbe49827f99","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2482aa33cf220","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"5G waa mid ka mid ah horumarada ugu weyn ee sanadkan, taas oo ah mid u suurtagelineysa aaladaha IoT inay xogta ku diraan iyo ku helaan xawaare aad u sareeya. Isku xirkaani wuxuu si weyn u kordhin doonaa awoodda aaladaha casriga ah sida kuwa magaaloyinka casriga ah iyo adeegyada caafimaadka fog, iyadoo yareyneysa culeyska isku xirka kana dhigeysa mid aad u hufan ("},{"_key":"2482aa33cf221","_type":"span","marks":["4646a770050d"],"text":"iBaseIT"},{"_key":"2482aa33cf222","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", "},{"_key":"2482aa33cf223","_type":"span","marks":["ff953500c0f2"],"text":"IntelliStride"},{"_key":"2482aa33cf224","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":")."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"4646a770050d","_type":"link","href":"https://www.ibaseit.com/"},{"_key":"ff953500c0f2","_type":"link","href":"https://www.intellistride.com/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"885114768267","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"048ed7d864640","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Aaladaha Digital Twin iyo Saameynta Ay Ku Leeyihiin Maareynta Casriga ah"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"939220ad8ab7","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f24e62a8c57f0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Aaladaha ‘digital twin’ waa aalado si toos ah ula socda walxaha jira, iyagoo si dhab ah u matalaya xaaladda iyo isticmaalka. Aaladahan waxaa loo adeegsadaa warshadaha kala duwan sida caafimaadka, warshadaha wax soo saarka, iyo maamulka gaadiidka. Waxa ay kor u qaadaan hufnaanta hawlgalka waxayna sahlayaan sameynta go’aamo ku saleysan xog dhab ah ("},{"_key":"f24e62a8c57f1","_type":"span","marks":["9b2a2fc62601"],"text":"Waverley"},{"_key":"f24e62a8c57f2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":")."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"9b2a2fc62601","_type":"link","href":"https://www.waverleysoftware.com/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c8ced476264d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"6762757279cf0","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Amniga iyo Qarsoodiga IoT"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"8dc9c1b892ff","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"828387ea80530","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Iyadoo kororka aaladaha IoT uu soo kordhiyo fursadaha tiknoolajiyada, amniga xogta ayaa sidoo kale noqday mid muhiim ah. Aaladaha blockchain ayaa loo adeegsadaa si loo ilaaliyo xogta, iyadoo la adeegsanayo nidaamyo gaar ah oo ah kuwa qarsoon. Nidaamyadan cusub waxay difaacaan xogta waxayna xaqiijiyaan in macluumaadka aan la beddeli karin, taas oo ka hortageysa weerarada cyber-ka ("},{"_key":"828387ea80531","_type":"span","marks":["a65458fea0fc"],"text":"IBaseIT"},{"_key":"828387ea80532","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":")."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"a65458fea0fc","_type":"link","href":"https://www.ibaseit.com/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"3cc34c0112a1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"16a64b0d11550","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Gunaanad"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"dd3d2413d6e1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"050f157d36200","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Tiknoolojiyada IoT ayaa sii wadaysa inay saameyn weyn ku yeelato nolosha casriga ah iyo warshadaha kala duwan. Horumarada IoT ee 2024 waxay leedahay fursado badan oo u suurto gelinaya magaalooyinka caqliga leh, adeegsiga awoodda geeska, iyo isticmaalka AI si loo hubiyo habsami u socodka adeegyada. JTech, waxaanu ka go’an tahay inaanu taageerno shirkadaha Soomaaliyeed si ay u gaaraan natiijooyin horumarineed iyagoo ka faa’iideysanaya horumarka IoT iyo tiknoolojiyada cusub."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"audio":null,"coverImage":{"asset":{"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[],"fallback":{"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/2af7e05bfbb7bb92613be3afaba8c32dd34b882e-1920x1080.jpg?w=1920&h=1080&auto=format","srcSet":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/2af7e05bfbb7bb92613be3afaba8c32dd34b882e-1920x1080.jpg?w=320&h=180&auto=format 320w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/2af7e05bfbb7bb92613be3afaba8c32dd34b882e-1920x1080.jpg?rect=1,0,1919,1080&w=654&h=368&auto=format 654w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/2af7e05bfbb7bb92613be3afaba8c32dd34b882e-1920x1080.jpg?w=768&h=432&auto=format 768w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/2af7e05bfbb7bb92613be3afaba8c32dd34b882e-1920x1080.jpg?w=1024&h=576&auto=format 1024w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/2af7e05bfbb7bb92613be3afaba8c32dd34b882e-1920x1080.jpg?rect=0,1,1920,1079&w=1366&h=768&auto=format 1366w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/2af7e05bfbb7bb92613be3afaba8c32dd34b882e-1920x1080.jpg?w=1600&h=900&auto=format 1600w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/2af7e05bfbb7bb92613be3afaba8c32dd34b882e-1920x1080.jpg?w=1920&h=1080&auto=format 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#043c74","width":1920,"height":1080}},"alt":"sax"},"categories":[{"id":"-8484f1c5-5fe5-5a6e-88ad-aec85b8ee873","title":"Taariikh","slug":{"current":"taariikh"}}],"author":{"name":"Maxamed Yuusuf","slug":{"current":"maxamed-yuusuf"},"profileImage":{"alt":"nnn","asset":{"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[],"fallback":{"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/l5a0ge0a/production/fb5c2670876b9388b76548379b96a0d97684db6